<td><img class="wp-image-11824 alignleft" src="Congratz%21%20-%20EDRi_files/digital_armour_internet.png" alt="digital_armour_internet" srcset="https://edri.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/digital_armour_internet.png 300w, https://edri.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/digital_armour_internet-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 88px) 100vw, 88px" width="88" height="88"></td>
<td>İnternette gezinirken daha fazla güvenlik – bilgisayarınızda: <strong>Firefox</strong> tarayıcısını kullanın. <a href="https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/new/" target="_blank">Buradan indirebilirsiniz</a>.<br>Ardından Firefox <a href="https://www.eff.org/en/privacybadger" target="_blank">Privacy Badger</a> eklentisini kurun – Bu eklenti casus reklamları ve görünmez gözetleyicileri engelleyecek.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><img class="wp-image-11828 alignleft" src="Congratz%21%20-%20EDRi_files/digital_armour_social_networks.png" alt="digital_armour_social_networks" srcset="https://edri.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/digital_armour_social_networks.png 300w, https://edri.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/digital_armour_social_networks-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 88px) 100vw, 88px" width="88" height="88"></td>
<td>Telefonunuzda <strong>Firefox</strong> (<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.mozilla.firefox&amp;referrer=utm_source%3Dmozilla%26utm_medium%3DReferral%26utm_campaign%3Dmozilla-org" target="_blank">Google Play</a> veya <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/nl/app/apple-store/id989804926?pt=373246&amp;mt=8&amp;ct=mozorg-ios_page-appstore-button" target="_blank">iphone için Apple Store</a>)
 ile internette daha güvenli gezinin. – "Tracking Protection" seçeneğini
 açmış olduğunuzdan ve gizlilik ayarlarınızda cookieleri 
etkisizleştirdiğinizden emin olun.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><img class="wp-image-11826 alignleft" src="Congratz%21%20-%20EDRi_files/digital_armour_passwords.png" alt="digital_armour_passwords" srcset="https://edri.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/digital_armour_passwords.png 300w, https://edri.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/digital_armour_passwords-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 88px) 100vw, 88px" width="88" height="88"></td>
<td>Telefonunuzdan internette anonim gezinin: <strong>OrBot</strong> ve <strong>Orfox</strong> uygulamalarını kurun. Onları <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/developer?id=The+Tor+Project">PlayStore</a>'da (ücretsiz) bulabilirsiniz. Apple cihazlar için adı: <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/be/app/onion-browser/id519296448?mt=8">Onion Browser</a> (0.99 €)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><img class="wp-image-11823 alignleft" src="Congratz%21%20-%20EDRi_files/digital_armour_apps.png" alt="digital_armour_apps" srcset="https://edri.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/digital_armour_apps.png 300w, https://edri.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/digital_armour_apps-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 88px) 100vw, 88px" width="88" height="88"></td>
<td><strong>Signal Private Messenger</strong> ile aile ve arkadaşlarınızla daha güvenli mesajlaşma.<br>Onu <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.thoughtcrime.securesms&amp;hl=en">PlayStore</a> veya Apple <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/signal-private-messenger/id874139669?mt=8">Store</a>'da bulabilirsiniz. En yakın arkadaşınıza da tavsiye edin!</td>
